Document: VisualShaderNodeParticleEmit
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeparticleemit.rst
Summary: A shader node that emits particles from a configured sub-emitter with customizable parameters.

This node internally calls the emit_subparticle shader method. It will emit a particle from the configured sub-emitter and also allows to customize how its emitted. Requires a sub-emitter assigned to the particles node with this shader.
