Document: VisualShaderNodeParticleEmit
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeparticleemit.rst
Summary: Enumerates flags controlling which particle properties are initialized by this node.

EmitFlags (int):
- EMIT_FLAG_POSITION: If enabled, the particle starts with the position defined by this node. Default: 1
- EMIT_FLAG_ROT_SCALE: If enabled, the particle starts with the rotation and scale defined by this node. Default: 2
- EMIT_FLAG_VELOCITY: If enabled, the particle starts with the velocity defined by this node. Default: 4
- EMIT_FLAG_COLOR: If enabled, the particle starts with the color defined by this node. Default: 8
- EMIT_FLAG_CUSTOM: If enabled, the particle starts with the CUSTOM data defined by this node. Default: 16
---CHUNK---
